VolunteerOpportunity.SpecialInstructions:
To bell ring during Family Volunteer Day you must be a part of a "Family" unit which would consist of any group of two or more people who consider themselves a family." Family volunteering can be done by the whole family together, by one parent and one child or teen, by siblings together or by extended family such as grandparents, aunts, uncles and cousins.

We also ask of family volunteers to be friendly;
Please dress appropriate for the outside elements

VolunteerOpportunity.Description:
Volunteers are requested to:
1. Help welcome the fundraiser guests and offer assistance to their tables or other event areas;
2. Walk information from one area of the event site to data entry volunteers and staff.
